{"tid":2058922,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳澤滔: 好多素人/本土派文宣既共通毛病","createTime":"2020-06-10T13:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T14:17:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"49704c1597a43ac995996aada7baf700940929e1","tid":2058922,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chakto/posts/10157179153602793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchakto%2Fposts%2F10157179153602793&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa%2FkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=243cf43c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chakto/posts/10157179153602793</a><br />\n<br />\nChan Chak To<br />\n8小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n[選舉局外人心聲]<br />\n<br />\n呢期睇好多素人/本土派嘅文宣<br />\n大部份都係集中講泛民點廢/泛民點呃人<br />\n其實我想講我嘥咁多時間睇你篇水蛇春咁長嘅文<br />\n唔係想睇泛民點廢<br />\n<strong>泛民廢唔洗靠你話我知<br />\n我淨係想知你有乜特別，投你代表咗啲乜理念</strong><br />\n<br />\n我唔介意你吹噓下自己做過乜（東九得反噴泉一單都俾我講咗五六年😅）<br />\n<strong>但好多都無提到點解我要投你</strong><br />\n<br />\n講真，你鍾意批評人嘅，其實唔洗做議員㗎<br />\n做youtuber 做KOL 仲多人睇仲自由<br />\n<br />\n#不過輸咗嘅人講嘅嘢又可以唔洗聽嘅<br />\n#跟你做連選舉資助都攞唔到呀<br />\n<br />\n<strong>後加：再簡單啲<br />\n如果我連續睇三份屌泛民嘅文宣<br />\n我係唔會記得你哋邊個打邊個</strong>"},{"pid":"d35f36a4b18d9f5dfc4721e6dad670ff63b69745","tid":2058922,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"Leslie Ma #我以為泛民廢係fact嚟<br />\n<br />\nBrandon Yau 不如誠實少少，選左你有咩可以做到？當你真心答，諗起所有犧牲左嘅無名抗爭者，條問題就會變得好沉重。<br />\n<br />\n仇恨好容易，言行一致好難。"},{"pid":"482b679036fb5ab92aaaa1dfcb4274f22fdc16aa","tid":2058922,"uid":151313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f059992361d1009eb6697560ed8b38ae7375a8f2","tid":2058922,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"482b679036fb5ab92aaaa1dfcb4274f22fdc16aa","tid":2058922,"uid":151313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy